{
  "id": "drilldown-logs-add-log-dashboard",
  "title": "Add Logs Drilldown visualization to a dashboard",
  "blocks": [
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "Dashboards give you an at-a-glance view of your data and let you track metrics through different visualizations."
    },
    {
      "type": "markdown",
      "content": "To add a Logs Drilldown visualization to a dashboard, complete the following steps:"
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "multistep",
          "content": "On the toolbar at the top of the Explore page, click **Add > Add to dashboard**, then click **Open dashboard**.\n\nThe visualization appears in a dashboard.",
          "steps": [
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "button:contains('Add')"
            },
            {
              "action": "highlight",
              "reftarget": "[role='menuitem']:contains('Add to dashboard')"
            },
            {
              "action": "button",
              "reftarget": "Open dashboard"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "interactive",
          "action": "highlight",
          "reftarget": "button[data-testid='data-testid Save dashboard button']",
          "content": "Click **Save** located in the upper-right of the page.",
          "requirements": [
            "exists-reftarget"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "Enter a title and description for your dashboard."
        },
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "Select a folder, if applicable."
        },
        {
          "type": "markdown",
          "content": "Click **Save**."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
